{"MYZONTES":[{"def":"The Marsipobranchiata.","pos":""}],"MYZOSTOMATA":[{"def":"An order of curious parasitic worms found on crinoids.","pos":""},{"def":"N, the fourteenth letter of English alphabet, is a vocal consonent, and, in allusion to its mode of formation, is called the dentinasal or linguanasal consonent.","pos":""}]}